Introduction/Business Problem
This assignment demonstrate the knowledge acquire during this course "Applied Data Science Capstone" that allow to strip
of the necessary information to evaluate and solve an existing situation within a business. During the course we explored
to majoe cosmopolitan cities: New York and Toronto, looking at their neighborhoods and able to represent them in a map.
The extration of these neighborhoods coordinates from previous files and sort them and added to the coresponding city map
for the purpose of visualization.

The business problem, when visitors visited any of these cities are not able to see the different distribuition of any site
of interest like neighborhoods and any feature associated with them, and where they are located according to the map. An
important point of reference for a visitor. How this problem can be solve?. I plan to used the geographical location of the
neighborhood and place them in the corresponding city map for visualization using the tools giving by this course.
